  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a medium bowl, combine shrimp, Greek yogurt, olive oil, garlic, dill, salt, and black pepper. Mix well to combine.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix breadcrumbs and feta cheese.",
    "Add the breadcrumb mixture to the shrimp mixture and mix until just combined.",
